SETUP NOTES
------------
1. Requires:
	rubygems
	hpricot
	open-uri
	htmlentities
	strscan
	haml
2. Rails (2.1) is frozen
3. Configure Hoptoad API key required in initializers/hoptoad.rb
4. Configure gem path in environment.rb
5. Not tested with Phusion Passenger
6. Configure .htaccess for FastCGI deployment
7. Configure proper address or domain paths on application layout
8. Call Site class methods to start crawling
	example:	script/runner -e development "Site.update_all"
			
			
